text: @UPSHelp I am livid. I had an expensive order due today and waited all day for it to come to be told at the last minute it was not arriving and had changed status to arriving tomorrow. After I'd had a text saying it was due today. What are you going to do to fix this?

@loookjones I completely understand your concerns and frustrations with this and would like to take a look into the details further for you. Please use the link to DM us the tracking number and details. ^CK https://t.co/wKJHDXWGRQ
